Joan Valerie https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Joan_Valerie 0 Joan Valerie (July 15, 1911 in Rhinelander, Wisconsin - January 30, 1983 in Long Beach, California) was a Greek-American actress, who appeared mainly in B movies in the late 1930s and 1940s.
